Dutch

English
Violet Weston (Meryl Streep) has cancer and a propensity for pills and alcohol.
She's a difficult woman to deal with and her husband has finally had enough.
Violet's family gathers including youngest daughter Ivy, middle daughter Karen,
eldest daughter Barbara, and her sister Mattie Fae. A family tragedy causes
tensions to run high and secrets to come out. The Weston women will be forced
to examine themselves and their lives whether they want to or not. Welcome to
Osage County, Oklahoma in the sweltering heat of August.
